wods.workout: This is a team workout, with one person working at a time. Reps displayed is to be split up between each team member. 20 min AMRAP: 10 c2b, 10 cals row then 20 c2b, 20 cals row then 30 c2b, 30 cals row. Keep adding 10 reps to the pullups and cals after you finish set.
wods.score: Score is total number of reps performed
wods.reviews: Jen: Partnered with Alex! I really enjoyed this and feel Alex did as well. Love when I can have so much fun during a work out!!!

wods.workout: Diane, 21-15-9 reps for time, and the lifts are deadlift at (225/155) and HSPU. Time cap is 20 mins. After you finish all reps perform a farmers carry at your weight of choice with either kettle bells or dumbells for 400m.
wods.reviews: Steve: I always look forward to doing some heavy lifting!!! HSPU are not my thing, but this is the practice I needed to get better at them, thank you Diane for a great workout!!!
